---
title: Carb Smart Roasted Butternut Squash Harvest Salad with Candied Bacon and Apple
description: Thyme-roasted squash tossed with a lovely fresh salad is the epitome of fall fare. Topped with salty cheese and crispy bacon, and perfectly matched with sweet apple, this dinner has it all!
